				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/B%E1%BA%A1ch-ti%E1%BB%83u/poem-OCO5C4um2xdP3aPD_OYJEQ">Bạch tiểu - 白小</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/C%E1%BA%A7m-%C4%91%C3%A0i/poem-dSnmLveHQYvLVD8-n4k18A">Cầm đài - 琴臺</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tr%C3%A3i/Chu-trung-ng%E1%BA%ABu-th%C3%A0nh-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-cXnmhYRwBeisJiNP_qzLEQ">Chu trung ngẫu thành kỳ 2 - 舟中偶成其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tr%C3%A3i/author-NlHfXoUXzue8FcsdIodRLQ">Nguyễn Trãi</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BB%91ng-Danh-L%C3%A3ng/Cung-ho%E1%BA%A1-ng%E1%BB%B1-ch%E1%BA%BF-t%E1%BB%A9-Tri%E1%BB%81u-Ti%C3%AAn-L%C6%B0u-C%E1%BA%A7u-An-Nam-ch%C6%B0-qu%E1%BB%91c-s%E1%BB%A9-th%E1%BA%A7n-thi/poem-0duL75_86doyE87vetnPtQ">Cung hoạ ngự chế tứ Triều Tiên, Lưu Cầu, An Nam chư quốc sứ thần thi - 恭和御制賜朝鮮琉球安南諸國使臣詩</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BB%91ng-Danh-L%C3%A3ng/author-ybCQBh0AFD5cfxUSJmxf8Q">Tống Danh Lãng</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/H%C3%A0nh-v%C4%A9-1/poem-FAKjeS5Ez_5nPUGzDq7JYA">Hành vĩ 1 - 行葦 1</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/author-Ghtg3UHpaIYXCkHiqunT7w">Khổng Tử</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/Ho%C3%A0ng-c%E1%BB%AD-nh%C3%A2n-b%E1%BB%8B-t%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-ng%C6%B0u-t%E1%BB%ADu-lai-y%E1%BA%BFt/poem-yT2T_5WLmsZQedp50K8fLA">Hoàng cử nhân bị tương ngưu tửu lai yết - 黃舉人備將牛酒來謁</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/author-JHbQVfC53E2lRJL-xE616A">Nguyễn Khuyến</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/Ho%C3%A0ng-h%C4%A9-8/poem-0yrpkNtlZ52VDCGRsJinxQ">Hoàng hĩ 8 - 皇矣 8</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/author-Ghtg3UHpaIYXCkHiqunT7w">Khổng Tử</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B9ng-Thi%E1%BB%87n-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/H%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-C%E1%BA%A7n/poem-QCImaCOLRfu1iOxKZPFc6g">Hương Cần - 香芹</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B9ng-Thi%E1%BB%87n-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/author-ZzgazbvW_31Yn18OxsV6nA">Tùng Thiện Vương</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Nh%C3%A2n-T%C3%B4ng/L%C3%A2m-chung-di-chi%E1%BA%BFu/poem-I86uGQtK3uDAayDqWSRvWw">Lâm chung di chiếu - 臨終遺詔</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Nh%C3%A2n-T%C3%B4ng/author-sMXrZTDvW5uflSvv6NTMXQ">Lý Nhân Tông</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-H%E1%BB%95/S%C6%A1n-th%E1%BB%8B-t%C3%ACnh-lam/poem-WN-42FNRca-zDpeAR7jL6g">Sơn thị tình lam - 山市晴嵐</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-H%E1%BB%95/author-qsdCXtvu8PM8SdkWmraV5A">Phạm Đình Hổ</a>)<br></div>	</div>
